flowchart TB
    start([launchd invokes daemon-tick every 30 min]) --> logging[Setup logging to daemon.log]
    logging --> dotenv[load_dotenv ~/.ambient/.env]
    dotenv --> gate1{API key set?}
    gate1 -- No --> skip1[Log: no API key, exit]
    gate1 -- Yes --> load_state[Load DaemonState from state.json]
    load_state --> cursor[Convert cursor to datetime]
    cursor --> read[read_events since cursor]
    read --> gate2{New events?}
    gate2 -- No --> gate3_no{Acquire lock?}
    gate2 -- Yes --> gate3{Acquire lock?}
    gate3 -- No --> skip3[Log: locked, exit]
    gate3 -- Yes --> analyze[Run analysis pipeline]
    gate3_no -- No --> skip3
    gate3_no -- Yes --> summaries_no[Check summaries catch-up]

    analyze --> update_cursor[Update cursor to latest ts_start + 1]
    update_cursor --> increment[Increment events_since_calibration]
    increment --> save1[Save state immediately]
    save1 --> summaries[Check summaries catch-up]
    summaries --> recal[Check recalibration]
    recal --> save2[Save state again]
    save2 --> done[Log: tick complete]
    done --> release[Release lock]

    summaries_no --> save_no[Save state]
    save_no --> release_no[Release lock]

    subgraph analysis [Analysis Pipeline]
        direction TB
        detect_comp[detect_compression] --> detect_pause[classify pauses]
        detect_pause --> narrate[narrate_batch via Haiku API]
        narrate --> append[Append to analysis-YYYY-MM-DD.jsonl]
    end

    analyze --> analysis
